14
00:01:33,490 --> 00:01:37,480
=My Calorie Boy=

15
00:01:38,067 --> 00:01:40,947
=Episode 16=
(Found You, Give-up Virtuoso)

16
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:54,840
Here she comes!

17
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,040
Xu Jingjing is going
to give us a big one!

18
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,040
Great!

19
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,680
Great!

20
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:21,759
Jingjing!

21
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,039
Jingjing!

22
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,680
Are you all right?

23
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:26,759
Let's go!

24
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,240
Oh, no!

25
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:32,520
I think Xu Jingjing is hurt.

26
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,159
Oh, no! Come on! Hurry!

27
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,120
Let's go! Hurry!

28
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,639
Move!

29
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,639
-Hurry!
-Go!

30
00:02:40,780 --> 00:02:44,140
(School Culture and Art Festival)

31
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,919
Where does it hurt? Can you move?

32
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,000
What was that, Xu Jingjing?

33
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,400
No...

34
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,439
I didn't mean to...

35
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:51,520
You did it on purpose!

36
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,240
You just want to see me

37
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,800
embarrass myself
in front of the entire school!

38
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,319
Everything about Alice and the whale

39
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,759
was all lies!

40
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:57,960
I didn't mean to do that, Jingjing!
You have to believe me!

41
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,840
I didn't mean to!

42
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,080
You did!

43
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,199
Do you know how hard it was

44
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:01,919
to convince my mom

45
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,400
to come and see my performance?

46
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,439
I...

47
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,080
Jingjing,

48
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,360
I followed the spikes.

49
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,319
But I don't know why

50
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,240
I knocked into you...

51
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,360
The Cheerleading Team
had no obligation to perform

52
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,319
with you guys

53
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:11,639
for the Culture and Art Festival.

54
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,919
I convinced my teammates and the teacher

55
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,000
to do it.

56
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,000
I helped you!

57
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,840
Why did you do this to me?

58
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:18,319
There's no proof

59
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,479
that Xu Jingjing
did this on purpose right now.

60
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,080
Let's not jump to conclusions.

61
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,319
I can't listen to this anymore.

62
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,479
What gives you the right
to blame Jingjing?

63
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:25,039
Do you have persecution mania?

64
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:25,719
Maybe you're the one

65
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,039
who stood at the wrong place.

66
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,879
I have the most stage experience!

67
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,599
There's no way
I would've been in the wrong position!

68
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,199
Jingjing!

69
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:32,800
Jingjing!

70
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,400
How are you feeling?

71
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,240
Where did you hurt yourself?

72
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,240
Is it painful?

73
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,240
Your leg is swollen!

74
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,240
What are you waiting for?

75
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:38,599
We have to take her
to the hospital immediately!

76
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,080
Right!

77
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,319
Let's go! To the hospital!

78
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,439
Take everyone back inside.

79
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,000
Let's go back inside.

80
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,700
(Outpatient)

81
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,120
On the surface,

82
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,360
it appears to be a sprain.

83
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,120
But

84
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,039
we'll need to do another MRI

85
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,800
to know the condition
of her ligaments for sure.

86
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,080
Doctor,

87
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:12,599
how long will it take

88
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:14,479
for her to fully recover?

89
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,839
Will it affect her dancing?

90
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:17,800
My daughter

91
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:18,959
is going to join the dance academy.

92
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,279
As I've said,

93
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,720
we'll only know

94
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,920
the exact situation of her ligaments

95
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,319
and if surgery
or normal treatment procedures

96
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:25,360
will be necessary

97
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,120
after we do another MRI.

98
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,439
I'll help you guys
make an MRI appointment

99
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,240
for tomorrow.

100
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,360
Thank you.

101
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,120
Thank you, Doctor.

102
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,639
How are you feeling?

103
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,759
Does it still hurt?

104
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:53,439
Do you think

105
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,600
Xu Jingjing is fine?

106
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,800
She probably sprained her ankle.

107
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,199
What if she actually
can't continue to dance

108
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:06,040
because of me?

109
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,040
Don't scare yourself.

110
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:12,839
Kang Jiawei,

111
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,279
do you believe me?

112
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,639
Of course.

113
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,560
You didn't mean to do that.

114
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:21,480
But she doesn't believe me.

115
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,720
Do you know

116
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:24,759
what I'm most upset about?

117
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,439
I helped her chase away those hooligans,

118
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,800
made her a headpiece,

119
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:32,319
helped her film the video
for her contest submission,

120
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:33,800
and I even sold

121
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:35,000
my dad's golden microphone.

122
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:35,920
I thought

123
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,279
we could finally be friends,

124
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:40,079
but she still thinks of me as an enemy.

125
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,199
Xu Jingjing,

126
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,079
was that move difficult

127
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,439
for you?

128
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:48,040
No.

129
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,439
But we only practised

130
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,319
that move

131
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,240
in the Taekwondo classrooms.

132
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:52,360
We've never practised it on stage.

133
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,720
That's why Gao Zhan

134
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:55,199
marked a spike on the stage for me.

135
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,600
But...

136
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,480
I don't know

137
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,519
why it went wrong today.

138
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,560
Liu Wan,

139
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:09,959
we'll cover

140
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:11,199
the medical expenses this time.

141
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,439
This isn't about money.

142
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:16,160
If something happens

143
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:17,319
to Jingjing's foot

144
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,439
and it affects
her college entrance examination,

145
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,279
are you guys going to be able
to take responsibility for that?

146
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,879
What does that mean,

147
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,199
Liu Wan?

148
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:23,920
Jingjing

149
00:06:24,079 --> 00:06:25,079
didn't do that on purpose!

150
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:25,639
Enough.

151
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,399
Don't fight.

152
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,439
Jingjing's well-being is more important.

153
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:15,680
That's her.

154
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,480
Xu Jingjing from Grade 11 Class 3.

155
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,800
I didn't know she was so vicious.

156
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,720
Coming up with such an evil scheme
to ruin Xu Jingjing.

157
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:24,399
That's why they say you can't judge
a person by their appearance.

158
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,199
Indeed.

159
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,439
But for you guys,

160
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:33,040
I can tell that you three
misrepresent facts

161
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:34,639
and distort the truth at first glance.

162
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:36,240
Let's go.

163
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:45,879
Doctor,

164
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:47,680
is everything all right?

165
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,480
Her ligaments weren't injured.

166
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,240
So

167
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,879
she can continue to dance ballet, right?

168
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:54,720
Mom!

169
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,759
Is that the only thing you care about?

170
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,240
Listen to the doctor.

171
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,279
She's young. With proper care,

172
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:01,319
she'll be able to exercise and dance

173
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,519
without any problems.

174
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,480
I'll prescribe some medicine

175
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,519
that'll improve her blood circulation
and remove blood stasis

176
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,800
to help her get better sooner.

177
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,360
Thank you, Doctor.

178
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,720
Everything is fine.
You'll be all right in no time.

179
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:15,079
Jingjing,

180
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,000
your foot

181
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,519
is fine now.

182
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,480
Do you want to let
Xu Jingjing know about this?

183
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,160
You tell her if you want.

184
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,360
Jingjing...

185
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,319
Dad,

186
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,399
you saw what happened yesterday.

187
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,600
Do you still think

188
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:37,080
she did it on purpose?

189
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,360
How about this?

190
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,039
Calm down

191
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,440
and think about it carefully

192
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,679
before you make a conclusion.

193
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,279
Okay?

194
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,440
Before we start,
I have two announcements.

195
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,480
First, good news.

196
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,279
Xu Jingjing's foot

197
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,720
is fine.

198
00:09:16,879 --> 00:09:17,559
She'll be able

199
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,600
to return to school soon.

200
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:21,720
The other matter

201
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:23,200
is the most anticipated

202
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:24,399
placement exam.

203
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,000
Placement exam?

204
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,440
What's there to be excited about
the placement exam?

205
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,600
I haven't even said anything yet.

206
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,759
Don't be so agitated.

207
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,799
Miss Chen,

208
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:32,080
which class will you be teaching?

209
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,000
Art stream? Science stream?

210
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:34,519
I'll go wherever you go.

211
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,240
This is

212
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,679
a preliminary placement interest form.

213
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,000
Go back

214
00:09:40,279 --> 00:09:41,360
and fill in the colleges and courses

215
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,120
you're interested in applying for.

216
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:43,679
Based

217
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,200
on what you wrote in the form

218
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,559
and your results,

219
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,440
I will give my suggestions and advice

220
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:48,720
on whether you should go into
the art stream or the science stream.

221
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,679
For those with better grades,

222
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,559
you can consider

223
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,399
if you want to join

224
00:09:53,519 --> 00:09:54,399
the advanced classes.

225
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,799
Not hungry?

226
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,360
Maybe put some mayonnaise on it?

227
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,559
Finally made you laugh.

228
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,600
Jingjing is fine.

229
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:23,200
So don't torture yourself anymore.

230
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,279
Jingjing is upset

231
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,759
because she was wrongly accused.

232
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:29,919
You've heard
of fighting fire with fire, right?

233
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:30,879
You're upset

234
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:33,039
because Jingjing blames you
for something you didn't do.

235
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,519
So think about something worse.

236
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,200
For example, the placement exam

237
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:37,679
and applying for colleges.

238
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,480
Just use another pain

239
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,440
to cover

240
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,240
the current one.

241
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,200
Kang Jiawei!

242
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:44,519
You made me lose my appetite.

243
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,240
This is all your fault.

244
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,720
Well, you have to face it eventually.

245
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:48,879
How about it?

246
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,840
Have you guys decided
which stream you'll be joining?

247
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,039
I plan on taking the college entrance
exam for art students,

248
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,240
so I'm going with art, of course.

249
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:55,320
But I want to join the advanced class.

250
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:56,960
I don't mind either.

251
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,600
I'm happy with any course

252
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,600
as long as

253
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,279
a university in Beijing accepts me.

254
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,919
Why Beijing?

255
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,159
It's more convenient for her
to pursue Qi.

256
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,200
What about you?

257
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,840
I'm sure Jingjing will follow Gao Zhan.

258
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,519
But he'll join
the advanced class, right?

259
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,360
So

260
00:11:22,279 --> 00:11:23,480
are you going
to join the advanced class too?

261
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,840
I'm just thinking

262
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:34,480
about how glad I am that Jingjing's foot

263
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,600
is fine.

264
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,679
If it was bad,

265
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,519
then does that mean

266
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:40,960
that I crushed her dreams?

267
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:41,919
How is she supposed

268
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,120
to fill that interest form, then?

269
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:44,960
Just thinking about that has me scared.

270
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:13,840
Gao Zhan.

271
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,879
Why are you here too?

272
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,559
I thought something was strange,

273
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,480
so I came to take a look

274
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:21,960
and see if I could find any clues.

275
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,159
That's my sentiment too.

276
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:25,480
Look here.

277
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:36,600
A spike.

278
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,440
This is the spike

279
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:39,360
I made for Xu Jingjing to jump.

280
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,440
But look.

281
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:42,440
Someone moved it.

282
00:12:45,519 --> 00:12:46,360
You mean someone

283
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:47,840
wanted Xu Jingjing
to make a fool of herself.

284
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,559
How is your leg?

285
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,240
It doesn't hurt as much anymore.

286
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:10,559
