577
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,240
is that Jingjing

578
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:56,559
doesn't seem like
science stream material.

579
00:22:56,799 --> 00:22:57,240
Look at her.

580
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:58,880
Who says?

581
00:22:59,079 --> 00:22:59,799
Yes...

582
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,880
I'll support you

583
00:23:01,079 --> 00:23:02,119
no matter what you choose.

584
00:23:02,319 --> 00:23:03,079
I trust you.

585
00:23:03,480 --> 00:23:04,759
I trust and support you too.

586
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,519
Who is here at this hour?

587
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:11,880
Don't tell me that bride of yours

588
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:12,480
is here.

589
00:23:12,799 --> 00:23:13,720
Impossible. I told the bride

590
00:23:13,839 --> 00:23:14,920
she was not allowed to come to my house.

591
00:23:15,079 --> 00:23:15,640
The bride...

592
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:16,440
Jingjing,

593
00:23:16,799 --> 00:23:17,400
listen to me.

594
00:23:17,519 --> 00:23:18,440
Choose art.

595
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:19,319
Get an arts degree,

596
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:19,960
and we'll open

597
00:23:20,119 --> 00:23:20,880
a matchmaking agency together.

598
00:23:21,039 --> 00:23:22,279
You'll organise the events,
and I'll host.

599
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,039
Have you eaten?

600
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:25,440
Xu Jingjing,

601
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,799
a friend from school is here.

602
00:23:38,119 --> 00:23:39,200
That is pretty much

603
00:23:39,519 --> 00:23:40,920
what happened.

604
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,720
Sorry, Xu Jingjing.

605
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:46,039
You've gone too far, Wei Xue!

606
00:23:46,519 --> 00:23:47,920
I know what I did wrong.

607
00:23:48,799 --> 00:23:49,880
But can we please

608
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,480
keep this between us

609
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:52,799
and not let anyone else know?

610
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,559
So you're scared now?

611
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:56,960
Why didn't you think of the consequences

612
00:23:57,119 --> 00:23:57,920
when you moved the spike?

613
00:23:58,279 --> 00:23:59,279
You were right there

614
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,920
when I was being falsely accused!

615
00:24:01,079 --> 00:24:02,160
I already apologised.

616
00:24:02,319 --> 00:24:03,160
Besides, I only did it for Jingjing.

617
00:24:03,319 --> 00:24:03,720
So...

618
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:04,960
You didn't do it for her!

619
00:24:05,119 --> 00:24:06,440
Did she tell you to lie?

620
00:24:06,599 --> 00:24:07,759
Did she make you move the spike?

621
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:08,480
No.

622
00:24:08,599 --> 00:24:09,039
So you did everything

623
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:10,160
for yourself!

624
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:12,079
What are you saying?

625
00:24:12,799 --> 00:24:14,240
I've always wanted to ask you this.

626
00:24:14,599 --> 00:24:15,359
Why are you so concerned

627
00:24:15,599 --> 00:24:17,279
about what goes on
between Xu Jingjing and Gao Zhan?

628
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,000
Is it because you also
have feelings for Gao Zhan,

629
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:21,200
and being around Xu Jingjing

630
00:24:21,559 --> 00:24:22,400
is the only way

631
00:24:22,559 --> 00:24:23,519
you have a chance to get close to him?

632
00:24:24,119 --> 00:24:26,200
Don't spout nonsense, Xu Jingjing!

633
00:24:26,319 --> 00:24:27,000
You know very well

634
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,160
whether what I'm saying is true.

635
00:24:28,799 --> 00:24:29,480
Yes.

636
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:31,200
Xu Jingjing is a goddess to you

637
00:24:31,359 --> 00:24:32,240
and nothing like a country bumpkin

638
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,000
like me.

639
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:34,000
So how could I get a chance

640
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,319
to perform with Gao Zhan?

641
00:24:35,559 --> 00:24:36,880
But I did!

642
00:24:37,079 --> 00:24:37,839
So you got jealous.

643
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:38,880
Am I right?

644
00:24:40,319 --> 00:24:41,359
Can you stop using Jingjing

645
00:24:41,519 --> 00:24:42,160
as an excuse?

646
00:24:42,319 --> 00:24:42,799
When will you finally learn

647
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,160
to walk on your own?

648
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,559
Congratulations to Jingjing
on her return to Class 3!

649
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:05,839
Are you feeling better?

650
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:06,759
Much better.

651
00:25:07,319 --> 00:25:07,720
Does it still hurt?

652
00:25:07,759 --> 00:25:08,079
I'm fine.

653
00:25:08,079 --> 00:25:08,559
That's good to hear.

654
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,079
For you.

655
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:22,920
As thanks.

656
00:25:23,319 --> 00:25:23,960
It's sugar-free.

657
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:33,319
I did you such a big favour,

658
00:25:33,519 --> 00:25:34,440
and this is all you're giving me?

659
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,759
You like sweets, don't you?

660
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:37,720
You can have this.

661
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:40,240
You can't brush me off with this.

662
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,000
Don't you...

663
00:25:43,799 --> 00:25:44,920
Is... Is that all?

664
00:25:45,079 --> 00:25:45,960
Was that not enough?

665
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:47,640
Yes...

666
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,079
Yes, this will do.

667
00:25:49,599 --> 00:25:50,440
This will do.

668
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,319
I have this for you too.

669
00:26:09,519 --> 00:26:11,400
This doesn't hold a candle
to my handsomeness.

670
00:26:12,079 --> 00:26:13,240
What's with your drawing skills?

671
00:26:14,279 --> 00:26:15,519
Couldn't you have tried harder?

672
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,519
Improve your skills?

673
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,839
Kang Jiawei,

674
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:19,960
I worked hard

675
00:26:20,079 --> 00:26:20,759
to design this for you,

676
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,839
and that's all I get?

677
00:26:24,039 --> 00:26:24,960
Give it back if you don't want it!

678
00:26:25,119 --> 00:26:25,640
I want it!

679
00:26:26,319 --> 00:26:27,000
I want it!

680
00:26:27,559 --> 00:26:28,680
Did I say I didn't want it?

681
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,160
Master Kang,

682
00:26:36,279 --> 00:26:37,039
thank you

683
00:26:38,079 --> 00:26:39,160
for clearing my name.

684
00:26:39,599 --> 00:26:40,559
If it weren't for you,

685
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:41,400
I might've never been able

686
00:26:41,559 --> 00:26:42,480
to clear my name.

687
00:26:46,039 --> 00:26:46,799
But when did you

688
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:48,400
investigate the case?
I didn't know anything about it.

689
00:26:48,759 --> 00:26:49,720
Of course,

690
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,079
it had to be a secret operation.

691
00:26:51,680 --> 00:26:52,359
Let me tell you something.

692
00:26:52,599 --> 00:26:53,319
I questioned

693
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,720
a lot of people

694
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:56,599
and went through a lot of clues.

695
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,680
I dug deep and investigated thoroughly

696
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:01,599
before finally locking in Wei Xue
as the suspect.

697
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,920
All right, all right.

698
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,359
It's all thanks to you.

699
00:27:05,519 --> 00:27:05,920
Right.

700
00:27:06,039 --> 00:27:07,000
I will remember your kindness

701
00:27:07,160 --> 00:27:08,319
forever.

702
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:19,880
I question the people together

703
00:27:20,039 --> 00:27:20,960
with Kang Jiawei.

704
00:27:22,319 --> 00:27:23,880
Gao! You startled me.

705
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,119
What did you say?

706
00:27:26,319 --> 00:27:28,839
I said I questioned the people together

707
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:29,720
with Kang Jiawei.

708
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,000
That guy didn't mention me

709
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:32,119
at all, did he?

710
00:27:33,279 --> 00:27:34,200
And I was the first one

711
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,759
to notice that someone
had moved the spike on the stage.

712
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,680
That was the key to solving the case.

713
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,319
So that's how it is.

714
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:40,480
Thank you then.

715
00:27:40,759 --> 00:27:41,880
You really helped me out.

716
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:43,799
Oh, right.

717
00:27:44,319 --> 00:27:45,720
For the placement exam,
are you going to choose

718
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,799
art or science?

719
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:48,440
I have to study art

720
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:49,400
for the course I want.

721
00:27:50,039 --> 00:27:51,160
What course are you planning on taking?

722
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:54,759
What about you?

723
00:27:55,279 --> 00:27:56,319
Art or science?

724
00:27:57,599 --> 00:27:59,000
My dad wants me to pick art.

725
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:02,359
Good luck with the placement exam, then.

726
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:05,559
Xiong Shuai!

727
00:28:05,759 --> 00:28:07,359
Give... Give that Cornetto back!

728
00:28:07,799 --> 00:28:08,359
You...

729
00:28:08,599 --> 00:28:09,880
I bought that for Yaoyao!

730
00:28:10,079 --> 00:28:10,640
I licked it.

731
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:30,260
(Gao's Observation Notebook)

732
00:28:39,359 --> 00:28:39,839
Here.

733
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:40,720
Thank you.

734
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,039
How is your leg?

735
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:43,839
Much better.

736
00:28:45,039 --> 00:28:46,559
I have to thank you guys again,

737
00:28:46,559 --> 00:28:47,160
Kang Jiawei.

738
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,240
Don't mention it.

739
00:28:48,599 --> 00:28:49,519
Xu Jingjing kept going on

740
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:50,880
about how she was never going
to clear her name.

741
00:28:51,519 --> 00:28:52,160
With her intellect,

742
00:28:52,319 --> 00:28:54,000
there's no chance of her
finding the culprit herself.

743
00:28:54,279 --> 00:28:55,359
It had to be up to Gao and me.

744
00:28:57,720 --> 00:28:58,640
I still have to thank you two

745
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,720
for helping me realise
a friend's true colours.

746
00:29:01,359 --> 00:29:02,160
Well,

747
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,680
maybe she wasn't really a friend.

748
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:07,559
Actually,

749
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:09,880
Xu Jingjing is quite upset

750
00:29:10,039 --> 00:29:10,880
about what happened...

751
00:29:14,039 --> 00:29:14,680
I know.

752
00:29:16,319 --> 00:29:17,279
Everyone thinks she did it...

753
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,119
No, no, no.

754
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,160
More than what everyone else thinks,

755
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:23,559
your opinion matters more to her.

756
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:28,759
You have more friends

757
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,920
than Wei Xue.

758
00:29:31,759 --> 00:29:32,680
Let's leave that aside for now.

759
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:34,279
What stream are you going to choose?

760
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,200
Science.

761
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,599
You have to join
the advanced class then.

762
00:29:40,119 --> 00:29:41,240
I heard Mr. Tian from the Physics
Research and Teaching Group

763
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:42,839
is the one in charge
of the advanced class.

764
00:29:43,079 --> 00:29:43,960
She is strict.

765
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:44,960
I know!

766
00:29:45,519 --> 00:29:46,960
They say he is just like Madam Otose.

767
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,200
He is scary

768
00:29:49,359 --> 00:29:50,160
when he collects papers.

769
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:53,079
Who is Madam Otose?

770
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:54,640
Gintama!

771
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,319
You posted that on Douban, didn't you?

772
00:29:58,759 --> 00:29:59,240
Right.

773
00:29:59,839 --> 00:30:01,079
I almost forgot about that.

774
00:30:04,319 --> 00:30:06,319
(Grade 11 Class 3)
The use of these stylistic devices

775
00:30:06,799 --> 00:30:08,039
made the article beautiful

776
00:30:08,279 --> 00:30:09,119
and rhyme.

777
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:11,680
All right.

778
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,279
Jot down the key points.

779
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,839
We'll stop here today.

780
00:30:15,279 --> 00:30:15,920
Class dismissed.

781
00:30:20,599 --> 00:30:21,519
Xu Jingjing.

782
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:26,799
Why don't you take me home today?

783
00:30:51,359 --> 00:30:52,680
Miss Chen knows about everything.

784
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:56,240
The others will stop talking about you.

785
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:03,319
I was wrong to blame you.

786
00:31:04,559 --> 00:31:05,279
I'm sorry.

787
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,240
I just can't figure out

788
00:31:11,039 --> 00:31:12,240
why you were so certain

789
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,039
that it was me.

790
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:14,279
I already

791
00:31:14,519 --> 00:31:15,599
explained myself to you,

792
00:31:16,079 --> 00:31:17,359
but you just won't believe me.

793
00:31:20,119 --> 00:31:21,200
I thought

794
00:31:23,039 --> 00:31:23,599
things were different

795
00:31:23,759 --> 00:31:24,920
between us now.

796
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:26,039
I thought

797
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:27,319
we could be friends now.

798
00:31:30,119 --> 00:31:31,519
I read a book before.

799
00:31:32,599 --> 00:31:33,440
It said

800
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:34,880
that if two people

801
00:31:35,039 --> 00:31:36,400
were to become friends,

802
00:31:36,759 --> 00:31:37,400
they would need

803
00:31:37,599 --> 00:31:39,039
to forgive each other's original sins.

804
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:40,359
Original sin?

805
00:31:41,839 --> 00:31:43,240
If you want to become friends

806
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:44,599
with someone rich,

807
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,400
you'll need to forgive their wealth.

808
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:48,440
Isn't being rich a good thing?

809
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,519
But

810
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,440
if you're poor,

811
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:53,799
then their wealth

812
00:31:54,039 --> 00:31:55,319
might sting.

813
00:31:56,759 --> 00:31:58,160
So don't be jealous

814
00:31:58,319 --> 00:31:59,720
of what someone else has.

815
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:02,640
If

816
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,079
you want

817
00:32:04,279 --> 00:32:04,880
to be friends

818
00:32:05,079 --> 00:32:06,039
with someone beautiful,

819
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,240
you'll need to forgive their beauty.

820
00:32:09,119 --> 00:32:09,640
If you want

821
00:32:09,839 --> 00:32:10,640
to be friends

822
00:32:10,799 --> 00:32:11,720
with someone talented,

823
00:32:12,279 --> 00:32:14,039
you'll need to forgive their talent.

824
00:32:15,119 --> 00:32:16,119
Xu Jingjing,

825
00:32:17,079 --> 00:32:18,400
do you know

826
00:32:18,559 --> 00:32:19,440
what your original sin is?

827
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:21,880
Beauty

828
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,319
and talent?

829
00:32:25,599 --> 00:32:26,559
Happiness.

830
00:32:36,519 --> 00:32:38,119
Xu Jingjing, did you know?

831
00:32:39,039 --> 00:32:40,079
Every night

832
00:32:40,799 --> 00:32:41,519
after school,

833
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,799
when I'm practising ballet at home,

834
00:32:43,279 --> 00:32:44,079
I can always hear laughter

835
00:32:44,279 --> 00:32:45,119
coming from your house.

836
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,759
And every time I would wonder,

837
00:32:48,319 --> 00:32:49,759
how your family had so many things

838
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:51,440
to laugh about.

839
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:52,759
Were there really

840
00:32:53,039 --> 00:32:53,599
so many things

841
00:32:53,759 --> 00:32:54,920
to be happy about in this world?

842
00:32:56,240 --> 00:32:57,680
Well, it's because of my dad.

843
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:58,680
He can't stop

844
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:00,039
once he starts talking,

845
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,799
and my mom and I have to flatter him.

846
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,640
Your parents are always supportive

847
00:33:05,799 --> 00:33:07,279
of your choices and decisions.

848
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,079
You wanted to learn Taekwondo,

849
00:33:09,279 --> 00:33:10,440
so they let you go.

850
00:33:10,759 --> 00:33:11,920
You wanted to draw,

851
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:13,279
so they let you draw.

852
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,200
You didn't do well on your exams,

853
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,759
but they always believe

854
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:18,200
that you'll do better next time.

855
00:33:18,599 --> 00:33:19,200
Why does it sound like

856
00:33:19,359 --> 00:33:20,079
you're throwing shade at me?

857
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:22,359
I'm envious.

858
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:25,000
Your parents

859
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,240
always have your back.

860
00:33:26,839 --> 00:33:28,279
You always have the courage

861
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:29,599
to do what you want.

862
00:33:30,839 --> 00:33:32,440
Sometimes, I'm not just envious.

863
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:34,279
Sometimes,

864
00:33:35,559 --> 00:33:36,960
I even feel jealous of you.

865
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:39,559
I can never

866
