for what to expect.

997
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,920
Both of you are aiming to join
the advanced class for the art stream?

998
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,400
Of course.

999
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:36,719
I'll be the only one left, then.

1000
00:39:37,039 --> 00:39:37,599
Xiaobai,

1001
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:38,519
you have to work hard too.

1002
00:39:38,719 --> 00:39:39,119
Let's all try

1003
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,280
to get into the advanced class
for the art stream.

1004
00:39:40,800 --> 00:39:41,400
I'll pass.

1005
00:39:41,599 --> 00:39:42,320
If I make it,

1006
00:39:42,519 --> 00:39:42,960
I'll have even less time

1007
00:39:43,159 --> 00:39:44,119
to follow Qi.

1008
00:39:45,079 --> 00:39:46,039
Wake up.

1009
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:47,039
Now is not the time for you

1010
00:39:47,239 --> 00:39:47,920
to be idolising and chasing after idols.

1011
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:51,199
Stop filling your mind with nonsense.

1012
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:52,440
Good morning.

1013
00:39:53,559 --> 00:39:54,079
Morning.

1014
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:54,800
Morning.

1015
00:39:55,159 --> 00:39:55,719
Morning.

1016
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:58,800
Are...

1017
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:01,639
Are you guys headed to class too?

1018
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,480
I mean... What a coincidence.

1019
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:10,079
I'm on my way to class too.

1020
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:13,360
Jingjing,

1021
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,559
Xiaobai and I are going
to the canteen.

1022
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:16,239
Okay.

1023
00:40:16,239 --> 00:40:16,880
We'll head on first.

1024
00:40:17,159 --> 00:40:17,599
Bye.

1025
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,440
Have you had breakfast?

1026
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,599
Yes.

1027
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:33,880
What did you eat?

1028
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:34,800
Crepe.

1029
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:35,920
What crepe?

1030
00:40:36,639 --> 00:40:37,280
Chinese crepe.

1031
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:03,639
I picked these up on the road.

1032
00:41:04,079 --> 00:41:04,920
Have at them.

1033
00:41:07,159 --> 00:41:08,280
You need a favour from me?

1034
00:41:10,079 --> 00:41:11,119
If you don't want it, fine.

1035
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:14,199
What has gotten into you

1036
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,440
and Gao Zhan today?

1037
00:41:15,719 --> 00:41:16,360
What's the matter with you two?

1038
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:17,280
What did he do?

1039
00:41:17,719 --> 00:41:18,519
What did he do?

1040
00:41:19,599 --> 00:41:21,880
Why are you so worked up?

1041
00:41:25,599 --> 00:41:26,239
Xu Jingjing,

1042
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,559
I have something to tell you.

1043
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:28,519
Go on.

1044
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:29,760
My online friend is actually...

1045
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:30,679
Listen up.

1046
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,199
There are a few of you

