00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,960
who have yet to submit
the placement interest forms.

1048
00:41:34,159 --> 00:41:35,280
I'll name them now.

1049
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:36,920
Ni Dapeng.

1050
00:41:38,639 --> 00:41:39,320
Xiong Shuai.

1051
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:41,159
´╗┐Xiao Chunjie.

1052
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,159
Kang Jiawei.

1053
00:41:43,480 --> 00:41:44,119
Xu Jingjing.

1054
00:41:44,679 --> 00:41:45,719
Hurry up and submit them.

1055
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,119
Um, Miss Chen,

1056
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,159
I'll choose

