with this?

1066
00:42:11,559 --> 00:42:12,320
I...

1067
00:42:13,639 --> 00:42:15,079
I... I just want
to think about it a little more.

1068
00:42:16,119 --> 00:42:16,679
Oh, right.

1069
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:17,960
What was that about your online friend?

1070
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:18,679
