that I'm good at

1076
00:42:38,320 --> 00:42:39,559
or arts.

1077
00:42:42,239 --> 00:42:42,800
I'm curious.

1078
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,559
Why would you want to choose
something you're not good at?

1079
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:46,800
Because...

1080
00:42:49,559 --> 00:42:51,400
Because my best friend

1081
00:42:51,599 --> 00:42:52,760
will be in the art stream.

1082
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:56,159
You have to know

1083
00:42:56,639 --> 00:42:57,440
that true friends

1084
00:42:57,679 --> 00:42:58,239
won't be separated

1085
00:42:58,440 --> 00:42:59,199
by distance.

1086
00:43:00,079 --> 00:43:01,000
Isn't there a saying

1087
00:43:01,199 --> 00:43:02,360
that goes
distance makes the heart fonder?

1088
00:43:03,760 --> 00:43:04,400
Kang Jiawei,

1089
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:07,000
this choice

1090
00:43:08,159 --> 00:43:09,800
will decide not only
your college entrance exam

1091
00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:12,800
but possibly even the direction
of your entire life.

1092
00:43:13,239 --> 00:43:13,880
I cannot help you

1093
00:43:14,079 --> 00:43:15,320
make your decision, but...

1094
00:43:15,960 --> 00:43:16,960
I hope you won't

1095
00:43:17,159 --> 00:43:17,920
make a decision

1096
00:43:18,480 --> 00:43:19,280
on impulse,

1097
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:20,440
all right?

1098
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:34,079
Kang Jiawei.

1099
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:37,039
You submitted
your placement interest form?

1100
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:40,280
You...

1101
00:43:40,480 --> 00:43:41,639
- You...
- Is your leg any better?

1102
00:43:42,320 --> 00:43:43,079
Much better.

1103
00:43:44,119 --> 00:43:45,000
You...

1104
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:47,800
You still decided to go
with science, right?

1105
00:43:50,960 --> 00:43:51,440
That's great!

1106
00:43:51,760 --> 00:43:52,719
I chose science too.

1107
00:43:53,079 --> 00:43:54,119
That means we can study

1108
00:43:54,360 --> 00:43:55,440
and get into the advanced class
for the science stream together.

1109
00:43:55,679 --> 00:43:56,400
But...

1110
00:43:57,199 --> 00:43:58,239
I already promised Xu Jingjing

1111
00:43:58,280 --> 00:43:59,119
that I would help her.

1112
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:01,280
