into the advanced class for arts.

1113
00:44:01,840 --> 00:44:02,679
Besides, I don't think there's much

1114
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:03,760
I can teach you.

1115
00:44:07,280 --> 00:44:08,000
Xu Jingjing,

1116
00:44:10,079 --> 00:44:11,039
I want to ask you something.

1117
00:44:20,239 --> 00:44:21,760
Why are you imitating Xu Jingjing?

1118
00:44:23,119 --> 00:44:23,559
Why are you copying

1119
00:44:23,760 --> 00:44:24,880
what she posted on Weibo?

1120
00:44:28,280 --> 00:44:29,280
I don't know what you're talking about.

1121
00:44:29,559 --> 00:44:30,239
Xu Jingjing.

1122
00:44:33,119 --> 00:44:34,719
There... There's nothing

1123
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:35,679
