1124
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:36,719
You don't have to be embarrassed.

1125
00:44:36,920 --> 00:44:37,800
You can tell me anything.

1126
00:44:39,480 --> 00:44:41,239
I said I don't want to talk about this.

1127
00:44:41,920 --> 00:44:42,559
But don't you think

1128
00:44:42,800 --> 00:44:43,920
this is unfair to Xu Jingjing?

1129
00:44:44,199 --> 00:44:44,719
Is Xu Jingjing

1130
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:45,639
the only one

1131
00:44:45,840 --> 00:44:46,880
that matters to you?

